<li>Your father's kindness and wisdom will always be remembered.  Holding you in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>My heart goes out to you and your family during this difficult time.  May you find peace in the days ahead.</li>
<li>Sending love and strength your way. Your father's memory will live on in the hearts of those who knew him.</li>
<li>So sorry to hear about the passing of your father. He will be remembered fondly.</li>
